OL,3,C'Legal errors' made in Jamie Bryson
OL,4,Ccase, Appeal Court rules
OL,6,FThe district judge who dismissed a
OL,7,Fprivate security industry regulator's
OL,8,Fprosecution against loyalist activist
OL,9,FJamie Bryson was wrong in law, the
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal ruled on Wednesday.
OL,12,FLegal errors were made in reaching the
OL,13,Fconclusion that Mr Bryson had no case
OL,14,Fto answer on allegations of making a
OL,15,Ffalse statement during an
OL,16,Finvestigation into door staff
OL,17,Foperating in the north Down area.
