OL,6,FLord Justice Treacy said the judge's
OL,7,Fdecision was "unsound as a matter of
OL,8,Fprinciple and based on an acceptance
OL,9,Fof an incorrect legal analysis".
OL,11,FHe ordered the case to be sent back to
OL,12,Fthe Magistrates' Court for rehearing
OL,13,Fbefore a different district judge.
OL,15,FMr Bryson has been locked in a legal
OL,16,Fbattle with the Security Industry
OL,17,FAuthority (SIA) for the last six years.
