OL,6,FIn 2018 the SIA issued a private
OL,7,Fsummons against him over claims of
OL,8,Fproviding false information to the
OL,9,Fauthority.
OL,11,FA #450 invoice allegedly created by JJ
OL,12,FSecurity Services Ltd, a company where
OL,13,FMr Bryson was a named director, formed
OL,14,Fpart of the inquiries.
OL,16,FPrevious courts heard it detailed five
OL,17,Fmen being provided for six hours, at a
OL,18,Frate of #15 per hour, at a bonfire
OL,19,Fevent.
