OL,3,C'Legal errors' made in Jamie Bryson
OL,4,Ccase, Appeal Court rules
OL,6,FReacting to the ruling, Mr Bryson
OL,7,Findicated that he may take the legal
OL,8,Ffight to the Supreme Court.
OL,10,F"The judgment of the court regarding
OL,11,Fthe chair's delegation departs from
OL,12,Fthe legal authority of Lord Denning
OL,13,Fwhich has stood for 50 years," he said.
OL,15,F"Really the Supreme Court needs to
OL,16,Ffinally determine the matter, to avoid
OL,17,Fconfusion if nothing else."
